Jon joined NEA in 2006 and invests in consumer internet and enterprise software companies. He led the firm's investments in Aera, Blue Jeans Network, Brandless, DataVisor, Desire2Learn, HackerOne, Hearsay Social, OPOWER (NYSE: OPWR, acquired by Oracle), ScienceLogic, Snapchat, Swiftype, The Players' Tribune, ThirdLove, and Uber. Jon's perspectives on VC and entrepreneurship can be found at www.jonsakoda.com or on Twitter @jonsakoda







